{"TopicId":166189,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"LOAD CRAFT screen search box","CreatedByName":"Fyrem","CreatedById":57131,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-05T17:49:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Fyrem","CreatedById":57131,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-05T17:49:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nLOAD\u00A0 CRAFT\u00A0screen should have a SEARCH function....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\ne.g. a box where I can type\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cabbr style=\u0022border-bottom:none;\u0022 title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u0022\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Eand see all the ships I saved with the word \u0022\u003Cabbr style=\u0022border-bottom:none;\u0022 title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0022 in the name....\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nor \u0022Station\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nor \u0022base\u0022 ..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nyou get the idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Magzimum","CreatedById":167187,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-07T07:45:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe it should, but personally I never have that many ships in that list that I need a search.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, they are organized alphabetically, so if you use a system for the names (I use the destination at the first word - e.g. Duna, Mun, Jool) then ships are easy to find.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Joseph Kerman","CreatedById":176176,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-07T08:15:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always name my military planes with a \u0022K\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-07T08:52:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere were a lot of threads suggesting all sorts of search features for the game, all of them would be useful, craft search, savegame search, tracking station search etc etc. The only one we currently have is part search in the editor, which is less than useful for me personally.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeople need it, but there are so signs of implementing it in near future, at least not that we know of.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr is there a mod for that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"John FX","CreatedById":59415,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-07T11:57:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo obvious now I read the words. \u002B1 from me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FungusForge","CreatedById":148313,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-07T22:34:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223188620\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022166189\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221507366351\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr is there a mod for that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/145176-13-ksp-craft-organizer-vabsph-tags-craft-searching-ver-141-2017-06-12/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EThere is\u003C/a\u003E, although It\u0027s clearly the kind of thing that would be appreciated in stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T13:41:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI support this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also would like to see a search bar for the tracking station and savegame screen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JonathanPerregaux","CreatedById":152561,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T13:42:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBetter still, let me click on a part from the toolbox and filter craft that use that part. I have enough ships now that I\u0027m losing track of which ones have landing legs, wheels, chutes, probe cores, whatever.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XLjedi","CreatedById":175658,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T13:47:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it supported\u00A0directories (perhaps in the same fashion as sub-assemblies?)\u00A0you wouldn\u0027t need to search or put keywords in craft names.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-10-09T13:48:19Z\u0022 title=\u002210/09/2017 01:48  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 9, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by XLjedi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T15:25:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223190322\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022166189\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221507556558\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152561\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JonathanPerregaux\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, JonathanPerregaux said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have enough ships now that I\u0027m losing track of which ones have landing legs, wheels, chutes, probe cores, whatever.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m still for search functionality, but maybe you should change your naming scheme? Or do some additions to current names, eg. I have three similar rockets, one is simply called Brykieta Mk4, then there is Mk4D - this one has \u003Cb\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ed\u003C/strong\u003Eocking\u00A0port, then there is also Mk4R - with \u003Cstrong\u003Er\u003C/strong\u003Eecoverable first stage. Mundownik Mk4 is unmanned lander, Mk4K is manned.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust saying though\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T19:31:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223190423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022166189\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221507562752\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0naming scheme\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\njust don\u0027t be like me: use a naming scheme but change it every week \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}